{"tid":388682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺日本人只係一個垃圾民族?","createTime":"2017-09-05T15:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T15:41:22.000Z","uid":68626,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"404b4fe0990cc6efde93304b1d8673c26ea4f965","tid":388682,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"其實真係無乜優點<br />\n你話佢好禮貌<br />\n其實不知幾撚虛偽 反而香港人屌你老母就屌你老母<br />\n日本人就屌之餘扮到自己好似好有禮咁<br />\n飲食文化又垃圾 食埋晒D ON9拉麵 同將D食物放係一小舊飯上面以為好撚好食<br />\n再唔係就生食野當美食 無技術可言<br />\n平時拍D垃圾片又唔好睇 笑片唔好笑 鬼片唔恐怖 AV又變態<br />\n大韓民族大炒小日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafef712e902df1b9c9a2838e7f7eb10b8967814","tid":388682,"uid":22858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>負皮上一頁</strong></span>"},{"pid":"faed79ce1f8995d7d8a4927b6d986ba5f7a7443e","tid":388682,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>負皮上一頁</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到咪負皮上一頁囉"},{"pid":"f4846d12803286ee646b17ae37a37d9d43b72f89","tid":388682,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"扑左"},{"pid":"e324bd7bdd604ad76cd3614de6b7fc79dbfff500","tid":388682,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑左</blockquote><br />\n忠言逆耳"},{"pid":"6081e1b7e6f66a23b389b7fb2cda964218a55d67","tid":388682,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"香港民族世界第一"},{"pid":"a8343f48b3320a7b9aa239fcb3609b2b56934e59","tid":388682,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港民族世界第一</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"98768661b970123159f70669b79ad60e220ee06f","tid":388682,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"AV係世界級"},{"pid":"5864ca3ccb29f32ee28b4fe5f9432e8e802024e1","tid":388682,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"69f87fb995f24a275bc0564a52cff11d6e976cfb","tid":388682,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"好過班南亞蝗啦 連扮都懶得扮"},{"pid":"d05fc62bef7d2f0c3bf17579fb3482fb49f33db5","tid":388682,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請善用起底功能</span>"}]}